caption.title: Model fit as a function of the infectivity enhancement ( ϕ) and the co-transmission rate ( β d) to demonstrate the effect of strain interaction within concurrent infection.
caption.p: Other parameters have the baseline values in Table 2. A) the combined KL information distance (KL3); B) duration of epidemic; C) inter-epidemic period; D) attack rate. Within the whited triangular region of the bottom left corner, only endemics with constant incidence where the number of new infections is balanced by the number of recoveries are possible.
